{"tid":808190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"匿名官員稱美國內閣曾考慮把特朗普趕下台","createTime":"2018-09-06T07:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T02:46:11.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd208b85be7a67d432ceb6da15e15991201035f","tid":808190,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"匿名官員稱美國內閣曾考慮把特朗普趕下台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001079301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001079301&d=w5pgVsCMpZrOvdE%2B8kmc8i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a25ec4b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001079301</a><br />\n<br />\n一名匿名高級官員在《紐約時報》(The New York Times)發表文章，稱美國總統唐納德&bull;特朗普(Donald Trump)的內閣成員因為特朗普的「不穩定」曾討論利用憲法手段把特朗普提前趕下台的可能。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在一封罕見的匿名觀點文章中，這名官員表示，有「早期傳言」稱內閣成員曾考慮援引美國憲法第25條修正案，啟動一個允許內閣官員要求國會罷免總統的複雜程序。但內閣成員最終決定不走這條路，因為這可能引起憲法危機。</span><br />\n<br />\n那篇文章的作者表示，然而，由於擔心總統「是非不分」，很多高級官員正在努力「阻止他的一部分議程和他最糟糕的傾向」。<br />\n<br />\n這位官員寫道：「我們希望這屆政府能夠成功，並且認為這屆政府的很多政策已經讓美國變得更安全和更繁榮。但我們認為，我們首先是對這個國家負責，而總統仍在以一種不利於我們國家健康的方式行事。」<br />\n<br />\n「這就是為何許多特朗普任命的官員發誓要盡我們所能維護我們的民主制度，同時阻止特朗普的那些更錯誤的衝動，直到他下台。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普猛烈抨擊這些說法，稱發表這篇觀點文章是一種「恥辱」。白宮新聞秘書薩拉&bull;桑德斯(Sarah Sanders)呼籲這篇文章的作者辭職，並稱這位作者是「懦夫」。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》(Washington Post)資深記者鮑勃&bull;伍德沃德(Bob Woodward)以批判性眼光審視特朗普的著作《恐懼：特朗普在白宮》(Fear: Trump in the White House)將在這篇文章發布後數日面世。當年，伍德沃德與卡爾&bull;伯恩斯坦(Carl Bernstein)的共同報導曾在一定程度上促使時任美國總統理查德&bull;尼克松(Richard Nixon)辭職。"},{"pid":"09a5cab91cc931bc0a116d289bc2a6123d9a228e","tid":808190,"uid":29270,"like":43,"dislike":6,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"匿名，然後Times反侵侵<br />\n<br />\n公信力為零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2939a7fc35dd5a194e3c4602e560479b0143b38f","tid":808190,"uid":35815,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5b8e70e1b1442bd8d257928e3672e98917b4558","tid":808190,"uid":4783,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"總統先係elected，下面所有人都係打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣趕落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係有人想暗殺總統，俾副總統上?<br />\n咁就係國家安全問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2439960593713e1f7c1b2d31a7c16d87a12f18fc","tid":808190,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ed95a676f284631c006d89b22908faf84829f7","tid":808190,"uid":5715,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"匿名官員曾勸侵侵連任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590041b3fff002329b16c8da82093a8fbb4c209c","tid":808190,"uid":4783,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得係應該要公開佢個名呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同政變有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9bd1ca64f6deb5cc31725ba5c06046f1dd9cdf","tid":808190,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"匿名官員更指中國及紐約時報或成大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498a892a6fa7ace4dab8b326e5a8a7ccc7bc3885","tid":808190,"uid":62247,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"又要出黎講野又要匿名<br />\n出得黎發言就係想人地聽你信你講野架啦<br />\n匿名,消息人士,有情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b175a3418e231d919ac612f55d23b6ea134f5bed","tid":808190,"uid":93784,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"cite